  <title>Making Up Attendance for Weeks 1 &amp; 2</title>
  <text texttype="text/html">&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hi everyone,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you joined the course late, here’s how you can catch up and receive attendance credit:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol start="1" data-editing-info="{&amp;quot;applyListStyleFromLevel&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;orderedStyleType&amp;quot;:1}"&gt;
&lt;li data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;
&lt;div role="presentation"&gt;Watch the lecture recordings &lt;span&gt;(both weeks, or just Lecture 1 if you attended Week 2)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;
&lt;div role="presentation"&gt;Submit a &lt;strong data-start="171" data-end="204"&gt;1-page report per week missed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;
&lt;div role="presentation"&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you missed Week 2, please also include notes from the guest speaker session with Enrique Sallent&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deadline: &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Friday, Jan 23rd 11:59PM&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you have questions or aren’t sure what applies to you, feel free to reach out.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Best,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Arundhati Bandopadhyaya&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-ogsc="rgb(0, 0, 0)"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Teaching Assistant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</text>
</topic>
